WEBVTT

00:22.065 --> 00:24.807
[dramatic music]

01:56.681 --> 02:01.643
[man groaning]
[tense music]

03:40.959 --> 03:43.571
[alarm beeping]

03:54.843 --> 03:57.498
[door clicking]

04:16.517 --> 04:18.345
- [Professor] It was one of
the strongest applications

04:18.387 --> 04:20.521
we've seen in years,

04:20.564 --> 04:23.175
and your essay touched many
people on the committee.

04:24.351 --> 04:26.266
- Well, I just want
to say thanks again,

04:26.309 --> 04:31.445
for the support and
everything you've done for me.

04:31.488 --> 04:33.795
- You've proven you deserve
to be here, Rebecca,

04:33.838 --> 04:34.926
and you'll be a real asset

04:34.970 --> 04:37.189
to the Neuroscience
Nursing program.

04:37.233 --> 04:39.061
And I want to assure you
that there are people here

04:39.104 --> 04:40.584
who understand your situation.

04:41.455 --> 04:43.108
We're a very diverse group,

04:43.152 --> 04:46.460
and some of us have personal
experiences much like yours,

04:46.503 --> 04:50.986
with unique and challenging
family circumstances.

04:51.029 --> 04:53.075
I think we've covered
everything for now.

04:53.118 --> 04:54.946
We're very excited
to have you here.

04:54.990 --> 04:58.428
- I'm excited, a little
scared but very excited.

04:59.690 --> 05:01.518
I've never actually
been on a plane before.

05:01.562 --> 05:03.651
- It won't be a long flight.

05:03.694 --> 05:05.217
If everything's
covered on your end,

05:05.261 --> 05:06.958
we'll see you here on the 17th.

05:07.002 --> 05:10.092
- The 17th? That's
like a week away.

05:10.135 --> 05:11.441
- We've got a lot
of ground to cover

05:11.485 --> 05:13.356
to get you all caught up.

05:13.400 --> 05:16.054
This is a very
special circumstance

05:16.098 --> 05:18.579
and in order to make sure
you won't fall behind

05:18.622 --> 05:20.798
we'll need you here
as soon as possible.

05:20.842 --> 05:22.452
- Right, right, yeah.

05:23.627 --> 05:26.761
The 17th. I'll be there.

05:29.416 --> 05:31.983
[gentle music]

05:39.948 --> 05:42.690
[water bubbling]

06:01.926 --> 06:03.667
[phone ringing]

06:03.711 --> 06:04.668
- [Richie] You know what to do.

06:04.712 --> 06:06.191
- Hey, it's me.

06:06.235 --> 06:07.976
I was hoping you'd pick up.

06:10.761 --> 06:13.024
Look, I'm headed to work soon.

06:13.068 --> 06:16.941
And I was wondering if maybe
we could meet up afterwards.

06:16.985 --> 06:19.596
I'll be done at 3:00 so I
could come by yours after?

06:20.467 --> 06:21.511
I know you'll be up.

06:22.686 --> 06:24.514
Just check in, okay?

06:27.822 --> 06:29.389
I need to talk to
you about something.

06:35.220 --> 06:36.396
I love you, bye.

06:43.577 --> 06:46.580
[traffic whooshing]

06:52.455 --> 06:55.371
[quiet rock music]

07:04.815 --> 07:06.077
- Hey, everything okay?

07:10.081 --> 07:10.908
Becca?

07:12.432 --> 07:13.476
Becca?

07:13.520 --> 07:14.477
- Hey.
- Hey.

07:14.521 --> 07:18.002
- Yeah, hey, everything's fine.

07:18.046 --> 07:19.526
- [Mel] So, how'd it go?

07:19.569 --> 07:20.657
- What?

07:20.701 --> 07:22.180
- I thought you had
that call today?

07:22.224 --> 07:23.704
- Oh, yeah, it went great.

07:25.445 --> 07:27.272
They want me there for the 17th.

07:27.316 --> 07:29.492
- Shit, that's like next week.

07:29.536 --> 07:30.406
- Yeah.

07:32.539 --> 07:34.323
- [Mel] That's a
good thing, right?

07:35.803 --> 07:37.979
- [Becca] It's great,
I mean, it's amazing.

07:38.022 --> 07:39.154
It's just--

07:39.197 --> 07:40.329
- [Mel] You still
haven't told Richie.

07:41.548 --> 07:42.679
- He's in a good place.

07:42.723 --> 07:43.941
You know, I don't
want to jinx it.

07:43.985 --> 07:45.073
- If he's in a good place,

07:45.116 --> 07:47.031
then it's the best
time to tell him.

07:47.075 --> 07:49.294
He's your brother,
he'll understand, okay?

07:50.557 --> 07:53.124
[upbeat music]

08:17.235 --> 08:18.585
- [Operator] Your
mailbox is full.

08:18.628 --> 08:20.543
To listen to your
messages press--

08:20.587 --> 08:21.979
[phone clicks]

08:22.023 --> 08:23.198
- [Richie] I know what
you said the other day

08:23.241 --> 08:24.808
about not everything
being an emergency.

08:24.852 --> 08:26.418
And I'm not trying to freak
you out or anything like that

08:26.462 --> 08:29.378
because everything
is under control.

08:29.421 --> 08:30.640
But something's going on

08:30.684 --> 08:31.641
and I don't want to get
into it over the phone

08:31.685 --> 08:33.077
because you really
need to be here

08:33.121 --> 08:34.296
to understand what's happening

08:34.339 --> 08:36.864
and I really think
it'll blow your mind.

08:36.907 --> 08:38.126
[phone clicking]

08:38.169 --> 08:40.083
Pick up, pick up, pick up!

08:40.128 --> 08:42.086
Pick up, pick up,
Becca, come on.

08:42.130 --> 08:45.046
Don't make me beg, just come
over as soon as you get this.

08:45.089 --> 08:47.222
Like I was saying, if I
start getting into it,

08:47.265 --> 08:49.703
you're gonna think I'm crazy,
and it's not about that.

08:49.746 --> 08:51.879
[phone beeps]

08:51.922 --> 08:54.969
You really need to be here.

08:55.012 --> 08:55.883
I need your help.

08:55.926 --> 08:57.624
Please, Becca, I don't.

09:00.104 --> 09:03.586
[phone beeps]
[phone ringing]

09:03.630 --> 09:04.587
You know what to do.

09:04.631 --> 09:06.894
[phone beeps]

09:06.937 --> 09:09.592
[keys clicking]

09:15.772 --> 09:17.078
[phone beeps]

09:17.121 --> 09:19.733
[phone ringing]

09:19.776 --> 09:20.777
You know what to do.

09:20.821 --> 09:25.826
[phone beeps]
[Becca groaning]

09:27.828 --> 09:30.700
[upbeat music]

09:30.744 --> 09:31.658
- What now?

09:32.615 --> 09:34.225
- Richie left me
some weird messages

09:34.269 --> 09:36.140
and now he's not picking up.

09:36.184 --> 09:38.229
Is it okay if I just run
out and check on him,

09:38.273 --> 09:39.491
just get it over with

09:39.535 --> 09:41.232
and then I'll be back
in 30 minutes, tops.

09:41.276 --> 09:44.061
[Mel groans]

09:44.105 --> 09:46.368
- Fine, but you
gotta make it quick.

09:46.411 --> 09:48.544
It's gonna pick up in
here once the game starts.

09:48.588 --> 09:49.763
- I'll be right back.

09:50.764 --> 09:51.591
- Hey, Becca?

09:53.593 --> 09:54.898
Promise me you'll tell him.

09:58.510 --> 10:01.513
[traffic whooshing]

10:04.081 --> 10:06.649
[somber music]

10:16.572 --> 10:17.834
- [Driver] Rebecca?

10:17.878 --> 10:18.705
- [Becca] Yeah.

10:24.798 --> 10:27.888
[singing in foreign language]

10:27.931 --> 10:29.716
- [GPS] In 100
meters, turn right.

10:32.240 --> 10:33.110
Recalculating.

10:34.285 --> 10:36.157
- It takes us
straight to a detour,

10:36.200 --> 10:39.247
which just takes us to another
detour. There's no logic.

10:40.988 --> 10:43.120
Turn right, nope, it's closed.

10:43.164 --> 10:44.426
Go back this way.

10:44.469 --> 10:46.167
Guess what, we're
stuck in a loop.

10:47.124 --> 10:48.735
- [GPS] Recalculating.

10:48.778 --> 10:49.736
[singing in foreign language]

10:49.779 --> 10:51.476
100
[GPS beeping]

10:51.520 --> 10:52.913
[driver sighs]

10:52.956 --> 10:56.786
[singing in foreign language]

10:58.440 --> 11:01.486
[faint upbeat music]

11:16.588 --> 11:17.720
- [Becca] The music?

11:17.764 --> 11:18.634
I'm so sorry.

11:18.678 --> 11:19.896
- It's been going on all night.

11:19.940 --> 11:22.116
If it's not that music,
it's that vibration.

11:22.159 --> 11:23.944
It shakes the whole building.

11:23.987 --> 11:25.859
I know I said I wasn't
gonna call the cops again,

11:25.902 --> 11:27.774
but some of us
have to work, Okay?

11:27.817 --> 11:30.124
Some of us need a
little peace and quiet.

11:30.167 --> 11:31.255
- I totally get it.

11:31.299 --> 11:32.735
- I don't think you do, Rebecca.

11:32.779 --> 11:34.737
Because if you did, this
wouldn't keep happening,

11:34.781 --> 11:36.043
but it does keep happening.

11:36.086 --> 11:37.218
- Well I'm gonna go
deal with it right now.

11:37.261 --> 11:38.828
- No need, I called the super,

11:38.872 --> 11:40.743
he's gonna come here
tomorrow bright and early

11:40.787 --> 11:42.266
and he's gonna have a little
chat with your brother.

11:42.310 --> 11:43.137
- Why would you do that?

11:43.180 --> 11:44.747
- Because I've had it, okay?

11:44.791 --> 11:46.793
It's either your
brother or it's me.

11:46.836 --> 11:47.794
And I'm not leaving.

11:47.837 --> 11:51.667
- Great.
[electricity sizzling]

11:51.711 --> 11:54.017
- Excuse me, I'm not done
speaking with [sighs].

11:55.149 --> 11:56.672
These people are such trash!

11:56.716 --> 11:59.109
[door thuds]

12:01.459 --> 12:04.724
[blaring upbeat music]

12:07.596 --> 12:12.601
- Richie!

12:12.644 --> 12:13.471
Richie!

12:17.084 --> 12:18.259
What the hell?

12:21.523 --> 12:24.265
[dramatic music]

12:25.483 --> 12:28.138
[door creaking]

12:30.445 --> 12:31.272
No!

12:32.099 --> 12:33.013
No, no, no!

12:40.672 --> 12:44.851
No. [sobbing]

12:57.820 --> 12:58.690
- [Richie] Hey, thanks
for showing up finally.

12:58.734 --> 13:01.389
[Becca gasping]

13:05.697 --> 13:07.656
Hey, earth to--
[both screaming]

13:07.699 --> 13:09.049
- Richie!

13:09.092 --> 13:09.919
- Becca!

13:11.791 --> 13:12.922
- Cover yourself up!

13:18.275 --> 13:22.323
- I was having the
weirdest dream.

13:22.366 --> 13:24.716
- No, I thought
you were in the closet.

13:25.805 --> 13:26.675
- In the closet.

13:26.718 --> 13:28.329
- [Becca] You are in the closet.

13:31.375 --> 13:32.333
- Oh!

13:32.376 --> 13:33.551
[tape rewinding]

13:33.595 --> 13:36.337
[Richie gasping]

13:37.468 --> 13:38.295
Right.

13:40.907 --> 13:42.822
[ominous music]

13:42.865 --> 13:44.649
- What the hell is
going on, Richie?

13:59.926 --> 14:00.752
[Richie groaning]

14:00.796 --> 14:01.623
- Come on!

14:18.161 --> 14:18.988
Okay, watch.

14:23.036 --> 14:25.865
This is my third attempt.

14:27.170 --> 14:29.042
I'm writing everything
down in a journal,

14:29.085 --> 14:33.089
which is good, 'cause it's
really fuzzy up here, but.

14:34.308 --> 14:37.702
It's [laughing] it's
a total mind-fuck.

14:38.616 --> 14:40.183
You know, seeing yourself dead.

14:41.402 --> 14:42.446
It's just, I mean,

14:45.449 --> 14:50.454
wow, I've seen hallucinations
and shit but...

14:52.587 --> 14:56.852
This, this is [laughing]

14:56.896 --> 15:00.943
I mean, like, this is real.

15:00.987 --> 15:01.944
- Turn it off.

15:01.988 --> 15:03.685
- Wait, hold on, there's more.

15:03.728 --> 15:05.861
So I keep waking up butt naked

15:05.905 --> 15:08.777
and at first I
thought this was mold

15:08.820 --> 15:10.170
or something like that

15:10.213 --> 15:13.260
but I think it's something
completely different.

15:13.303 --> 15:15.653
As far as I can tell,
this is where it happens.

15:17.264 --> 15:19.483
Okay, this is where
it gets weird.

15:20.876 --> 15:23.618
[film crackling]

15:24.706 --> 15:25.533
See!

15:26.577 --> 15:27.970
Did you see that?

15:28.014 --> 15:31.582
I can't get it on tape
because it keeps messing up.

15:31.626 --> 15:32.627
But you were here,
what did you see?

15:32.670 --> 15:33.367
- What do you mean?

15:33.410 --> 15:34.455
I wasn't in the room.

15:36.413 --> 15:38.981
- You couldn't have come
over five minutes earlier!

15:40.983 --> 15:41.853
Wait, where were you?

15:41.897 --> 15:42.637
I've been calling you all day.

15:42.680 --> 15:43.943
- I was at work.

15:43.986 --> 15:45.683
When I got your messages
I tried calling you back

15:45.727 --> 15:47.207
but you didn't pick up.

15:47.250 --> 15:49.426
- Yeah, I don't know
what I did with my phone.

15:50.514 --> 15:52.038
You're here now, that's great.

15:52.081 --> 15:53.996
I need you to pay attention.

15:54.040 --> 15:56.433
Okay, just stay
there, one second.

15:59.915 --> 16:01.264
- Did you stop
taking your pills?

16:01.308 --> 16:02.135
- No.

16:03.310 --> 16:05.486
Yes, I like...that's
beside the point.

16:06.487 --> 16:07.357
What's wrong?

16:07.401 --> 16:08.576
Do you not see what's going on?

16:08.619 --> 16:09.577
- No, I do see what's
going on, Richie,

16:09.620 --> 16:10.839
and I don't have
time to get pulled

16:10.882 --> 16:13.450
into another one of
your weird art projects.

16:13.494 --> 16:15.583
God dammit, I thought
something happened!

16:15.626 --> 16:18.281
- Something did happen!

16:18.325 --> 16:20.327
- I want to be here
and I want to help you

16:20.370 --> 16:21.850
but I have to go right now.

16:21.893 --> 16:23.547
I'm done at 3:00, I
can come back here

16:23.591 --> 16:25.071
and we can figure
this out together.

16:25.114 --> 16:26.681
- Please, please, Becca.

16:26.724 --> 16:29.118
- Now, I can see that things
are really intense right now.

16:29.162 --> 16:33.557
Okay, all right,
but I'll be back.

16:33.601 --> 16:35.385
But I need you to
keep the music off

16:35.429 --> 16:39.302
and stop whatever this
is until then, okay?

16:40.260 --> 16:41.739
Okay.

16:41.783 --> 16:43.002
- Becca, I can't figure this
out without you watching.

16:43.045 --> 16:44.568
Okay, please, I just,
I need you to watch.

16:44.612 --> 16:45.482
Please, just stay.

16:45.526 --> 16:46.962
Don't, just look, okay, look!

16:47.006 --> 16:47.832
Look!

16:49.921 --> 16:51.532
[Becca gasps]

16:51.575 --> 16:54.230
[phone ringing]

16:56.885 --> 16:58.974
[Becca groans]

16:59.018 --> 17:00.932
- Hey, everything okay?

17:00.976 --> 17:03.587
- Yeah, it's worse
that I thought.

17:03.631 --> 17:04.980
- [Mel] Is Richie all right?

17:07.242 --> 17:09.289
- Yeah, he doesn't look so good.

17:09.332 --> 17:14.163
Ah, I don't think
I can leave yet.

17:14.207 --> 17:15.772
I'll call you back later, okay?

17:20.865 --> 17:22.345
What the fuck is
going on, Richie?

17:22.388 --> 17:23.825
- It's all in
here, which is good

17:23.867 --> 17:26.088
because things up here
are a little bit jumbled.

17:27.959 --> 17:28.786
Okay, see?

17:28.830 --> 17:30.571
- What the fuck is going on!

17:30.614 --> 17:32.660
- Just relax, okay, relax.

17:32.703 --> 17:34.488
- Relax? Relax!

17:34.531 --> 17:36.925
There are dead bodies all
over the apartment, Richie.

17:36.968 --> 17:37.839
Your dead bodies!

17:37.882 --> 17:39.275
- Just shut up, okay!

17:39.319 --> 17:40.929
I'm sorry, I'm sorry,
that was very mean.

17:40.972 --> 17:41.756
I love you.

17:41.799 --> 17:43.279
Look, just listen.

17:43.323 --> 17:45.977
I called you because
something bad did happen.

17:47.979 --> 17:49.198
I killed myself.

17:50.678 --> 17:53.420
But then something
amazing happened.

17:53.463 --> 17:55.074
- I don't understand.

17:55.117 --> 17:57.641
- I've already died three times.

17:57.685 --> 18:01.080
And I have come
back three times.

18:01.123 --> 18:02.211
But I don't know how.

18:02.255 --> 18:03.082
I thought the video
would capture it

18:03.125 --> 18:03.995
but you saw what happened.

18:04.039 --> 18:06.172
So I need you to be the video.

18:06.215 --> 18:07.738
- [Becca] What do you mean?

18:07.782 --> 18:10.263
- I need you in my room to
just watch what happens next.

18:10.306 --> 18:12.526
- [Becca] Okay, and
where will you be?

18:12.569 --> 18:13.962
- I'll be dead.

18:14.005 --> 18:14.789
- What? Wait!

18:14.832 --> 18:16.269
What do you mean?

18:16.312 --> 18:17.574
- I'm gonna kill myself.

18:18.880 --> 18:20.229
And I need you to be in here

18:21.361 --> 18:23.102
to just watch what happens next.

18:23.145 --> 18:24.233
- No.

18:24.277 --> 18:25.887
- Becca, please.
- No, no way!

18:25.930 --> 18:27.541
Don't you dare!

18:27.584 --> 18:28.977
Don't you dare!

18:29.020 --> 18:32.111
[somber music]

18:32.154 --> 18:34.504
[Richie sighs]

18:34.548 --> 18:36.985
[door thuds]

18:42.208 --> 18:45.298
[gentle jazzy music]

18:49.911 --> 18:51.173
[bass rumbling]

18:51.217 --> 18:56.178
- Oh, no you don't.

18:56.657 --> 19:00.313
[broomstick thudding]

19:00.356 --> 19:02.880
[Becca sighs]

19:04.447 --> 19:07.189
[dramatic music]

19:08.277 --> 19:10.714
[door thuds]

19:11.585 --> 19:12.934
- You came back.

19:16.067 --> 19:19.419
- Richie, this has to
stop, right now, okay.

19:19.462 --> 19:24.337
The music and whatever
this is, has to stop.

19:24.380 --> 19:26.817
- I'm not trying
to scare you, okay.

19:26.861 --> 19:28.732
I get it, this is really weird.

19:29.603 --> 19:31.344
But take a look around.

19:31.387 --> 19:32.519
I'm not making this up.

19:32.562 --> 19:34.651
I'm not spiralling,
this is happening.

19:34.695 --> 19:38.133
So let's just, you
know, go with it.

19:38.177 --> 19:39.569
- I'm not comfortable with this.

19:39.613 --> 19:41.397
- It's already done.

19:41.441 --> 19:42.616
- What's already done?

19:42.659 --> 19:44.008
- I took something
when you stepped out.

19:44.052 --> 19:45.749
So it's gonna be
kicking in pretty soon.

19:45.793 --> 19:47.360
- Jesus, Richie!

19:47.403 --> 19:49.579
- It's fine, it's fine, really.

19:49.623 --> 19:50.406
- [Becca] Oh my God.

19:50.450 --> 19:51.364
- No, no, no, I'm good.

19:51.407 --> 19:52.495
I'm good, really.

19:52.539 --> 19:53.888
I'm fine.

19:53.931 --> 19:55.933
[somber music]

19:55.977 --> 19:58.109
- [Becca] We need to get
you to a hospital, Richie.

19:58.153 --> 19:58.980
- Uh uh.

20:00.677 --> 20:02.244
You've seen my bodies.

20:02.288 --> 20:03.245
Just trust me.

20:04.986 --> 20:06.553
I'll come back, I promise.

20:10.034 --> 20:11.906
When I'm gone, go in my bedroom.

20:13.081 --> 20:14.430
Write down what you see.

20:20.001 --> 20:23.961
It's like when I had
heatstroke in Hampton Beach.

20:25.528 --> 20:26.355
- Not really.

20:28.662 --> 20:32.013
- You held my hand
all night long.

20:32.056 --> 20:35.277
[gentle music]

20:35.321 --> 20:36.365
- I remember.

20:43.329 --> 20:45.200
I remember when you
puked on my prom date

20:45.244 --> 20:47.158
before we even had
a chance to leave.

20:48.682 --> 20:51.424
'Cause you drank an
entire bottle of schnapps.

20:52.990 --> 20:54.644
- Darryl something.

20:54.688 --> 20:56.298
- Darryl Friedman.

20:56.342 --> 20:58.822
- [laughs] He had it comin'.

21:05.438 --> 21:07.483
- I remember last year when
I got a call from the cops

21:07.527 --> 21:12.532
at 3:00 in the morning saying
they took you to the hospital.

21:16.187 --> 21:18.146
How I felt when I
