44:12.040 --> 44:13.651
- Yeah, you'd be surprised.

44:15.000 --> 44:17.829
For a while I thought that
things would be different.

44:17.872 --> 44:21.615
But, he needs me,

44:21.659 --> 44:23.530
so here I am.

44:25.271 --> 44:27.839
- [Matt] Why isn't he here
helping you out for a change?

44:27.882 --> 44:29.101
- Well, I don't
know if you know,

44:29.144 --> 44:31.538
but Richie has some
mental health issues.

44:31.581 --> 44:32.844
- [laughs] You don't say.

44:35.107 --> 44:36.108
[gentle music]

44:36.151 --> 44:38.110
Okay, well, just
bend at your knee

44:38.153 --> 44:40.329
and lift with your legs,
not with your back.

44:41.722 --> 44:42.549
Come on.

44:49.077 --> 44:51.732
[both groaning]

44:58.783 --> 45:00.088
- Ah, thank you.

45:02.743 --> 45:03.657
- Anytime.

45:05.398 --> 45:08.183
[both groaning]

45:08.227 --> 45:09.619
That was the last time.

45:21.631 --> 45:23.329
- Hey, thanks.

45:24.286 --> 45:26.854
- Anytime [laughs], no.

45:28.813 --> 45:29.683
Good night.

45:30.989 --> 45:31.990
Keep it quiet, okay?

46:07.199 --> 46:09.723
[tense music]

46:15.337 --> 46:18.123
[ominous humming]

46:33.878 --> 46:35.140
- Hey, listen--

46:35.183 --> 46:38.012
- Please, just, can you
give me five minutes?

46:38.056 --> 46:39.622
I just, I need a break.

46:40.885 --> 46:41.711
- Sure.

46:58.250 --> 47:00.992
[dramatic music]

47:24.711 --> 47:27.540
- Jesus Christ,
Richie, the music!

47:38.768 --> 47:40.074
- Finally, you're awake.

47:40.118 --> 47:42.511
- [Becca] All I
wanted was five minutes.

47:42.555 --> 47:45.384
- That was more
than five minutes.

47:45.427 --> 47:49.301
- [groans] So I fell
asleep, so what.

47:50.563 --> 47:54.393
Mm, maybe we should
order pizza or something.

47:55.742 --> 47:57.135
Why are you acting so weird?

47:58.136 --> 48:00.486
- Becca--
[knocking at the door]

48:00.529 --> 48:03.489
- Shit, what did I say
about the goddam music!

48:03.532 --> 48:04.533
- Becca, wait.

48:04.577 --> 48:05.360
[fist banging]

48:05.404 --> 48:07.362
- What the fuck is that?

48:07.406 --> 48:09.364
- I was tryin' somethin' out.

48:09.408 --> 48:10.235
- Oh, God.

48:11.584 --> 48:12.411
- Becca!

48:13.325 --> 48:15.283
I have had it with you!

48:15.327 --> 48:17.155
I've been more than patient.

48:17.198 --> 48:20.158
You sucker me in with your
sad girl song and dance.

48:20.201 --> 48:22.334
Like a chump I fall for it.

48:22.377 --> 48:24.118
Well no more, okay!

48:24.162 --> 48:25.685
I'm callin' the cops.

48:25.728 --> 48:26.599
- He's gonna call the cops.

48:26.642 --> 48:28.993
- Don't open it!
- I have to!

48:31.125 --> 48:32.474
Hey, Matt, how's it going?

48:32.518 --> 48:33.867
- Bad, Dick, what do you think?

48:33.911 --> 48:35.956
It's the middle of the
night and I'm still awake.

48:36.000 --> 48:37.349
- Yeah, I'm sorry
about the music,

48:37.392 --> 48:39.786
I'm just clearing my head.

48:39.829 --> 48:41.614
- Oh, yeah, well you can't
do this to people, okay?

48:41.657 --> 48:42.441
I have rights.

48:42.484 --> 48:43.355
- We're so sorry.

48:43.398 --> 48:44.399
I told him to keep it down.

48:44.443 --> 48:45.879
- Oh, well that solves it then

48:45.923 --> 48:47.620
because this one gives two shitswhat you tell him, huh?

48:47.663 --> 48:49.056
- [Becca] Okay, you
know, the music's off,

48:49.100 --> 48:51.232
it won't be going on
again, it's all right.

48:51.276 --> 48:52.755
So, just go back
to your apartment.

48:52.799 --> 48:53.887
- What do you
think you're doing?

48:53.931 --> 48:55.976
Don't you dare close
the door on me.

48:56.020 --> 48:57.412
- Hey, get out of here!

48:57.456 --> 48:58.283
- Okay.

49:00.198 --> 49:01.025
- Ow.

49:01.068 --> 49:02.156
- Smells like death in here.

49:03.244 --> 49:04.942
I don't know what I expected
from the likes of you two.

49:04.985 --> 49:07.422
There's paint everywhere,
this place is a pigsty.

49:08.728 --> 49:10.208
What the hell is that?

49:10.251 --> 49:12.601
- [Becca] It's not
what it looks like.

49:12.645 --> 49:15.343
[dramatic music]

49:16.518 --> 49:17.345
- You made this?

49:25.353 --> 49:26.659
Holy shit!

49:26.702 --> 49:29.053
Holy fuckin'...you stay
the fuck away from me.

49:30.228 --> 49:31.925
Holy fuckin' shit!

49:31.969 --> 49:33.579
Hey, you get away from me.

49:33.622 --> 49:35.929
Jesus Christ, you are
fuckin' psychopaths.

49:35.973 --> 49:37.800
I knew it, I knew it.

49:37.844 --> 49:39.541
Oh, oh my God.

49:39.585 --> 49:40.890
- Matt, no, please.

49:40.934 --> 49:42.414
- You shut your mouth.
- Please, we can explain.

49:42.457 --> 49:44.720
- Explain it to the
cops, missy, okay.

49:44.764 --> 49:45.939
Step away from me.

49:45.983 --> 49:47.854
Stay the fuck away from me.

49:47.897 --> 49:49.073
- Please, please don't.

49:51.075 --> 49:54.295
[Richie laughing]
[dramatic music]

49:54.339 --> 49:56.080
- You son of a bitch!

49:56.123 --> 49:58.038
- If you'd just stop
and listen for a minute.

49:58.082 --> 49:59.692
- I just got this phone.

49:59.735 --> 50:01.433
You know how much this cost?

50:01.476 --> 50:03.609
More than your life.
- Don't!

50:03.652 --> 50:05.002
- Oh, I dare you!

50:05.959 --> 50:07.917
[blow thuds]
[Matt groans]

50:07.961 --> 50:09.223
[Becca gasping]
[Richie laughing]

50:09.267 --> 50:10.572
- Why would you do that?

50:10.616 --> 50:12.096
- He was gonna call the cops.

50:16.187 --> 50:17.579
- With what?

50:17.623 --> 50:19.451
Dammit, Richie, you keep
making everything harder.

50:19.494 --> 50:22.367
Why couldn't you just
listen to me for once?

50:22.410 --> 50:23.803
- I don't think
that's very fair.

50:23.846 --> 50:25.935
- And what were you
doing with that arm?

50:25.979 --> 50:27.067
- Well, I found
it in the bathroom

50:27.111 --> 50:29.678
so I just started
painting with it.

50:29.722 --> 50:32.420
I mean, come on, how fuckin'
avant-garde is that, right?

50:32.464 --> 50:34.988
- [groaning] You left
evidence in the living room.

50:35.032 --> 50:35.815
- What evidence?

50:35.858 --> 50:36.946
I am alive.

50:36.990 --> 50:39.079
- No one's gonna
think that's your arm.

50:39.123 --> 50:40.428
- It's an exact copy.

50:41.299 --> 50:42.952
[Becca sighs]

50:42.996 --> 50:44.780
- We've been through this.

50:44.824 --> 50:47.653
Your arm is attached
to your body, Richie.

50:47.696 --> 50:50.351
That one, it's not, remember?

50:50.395 --> 50:52.571
- Yeah, okay, okay, right.

50:54.747 --> 50:56.966
Duh, wait.

50:57.010 --> 50:58.229
Why don't we just kill him?

50:58.272 --> 51:00.013
- We're not killing anyone.

51:00.057 --> 51:01.188
- Just listen to me.
- No.

51:01.232 --> 51:02.624
- If we kill him--
- Richie.

51:02.668 --> 51:04.409
We are not killing him.

51:04.452 --> 51:06.846
- Hear me out, all right,
just give me a second.

51:12.417 --> 51:13.896
Lift him up.

51:13.940 --> 51:17.987
Lift him up, come on.
[Becca groaning]

51:18.031 --> 51:20.773
[dramatic music]

51:23.993 --> 51:26.605
[ominous humming]

51:26.648 --> 51:28.476
- You do realize this
is kidnapping, right?

51:28.520 --> 51:29.651
- It doesn't matter.

51:29.695 --> 51:30.739
None of it matters.

51:30.783 --> 51:32.611
It's gonna be like
a dream, right?

51:32.654 --> 51:34.221
If we kill him.

51:35.527 --> 51:36.354
- No.

51:38.573 --> 51:40.009
- He'll die here,

51:40.053 --> 51:42.011
then another him's
gonna come out of there

51:42.055 --> 51:44.101
and it'll be like
it never happened.

51:44.144 --> 51:45.232
- How do you know that?

51:45.276 --> 51:46.451
- Just trust me,
it all makes sense.

51:46.494 --> 51:47.626
- No, it doesn't make sense.

51:47.669 --> 51:48.801
None of it makes sense.

51:48.844 --> 51:50.107
[Richie sighs]

51:50.150 --> 51:51.499
You keep coming back but
how do you know that--

51:51.543 --> 51:53.588
- Everyone comes back, Becca!

51:56.200 --> 51:58.463
Listen, I didn't want you to
get caught up in this, okay.

51:58.506 --> 52:00.769
But I needed someone and you
are the only one I trust.

52:00.813 --> 52:05.122
- Oh, boohoo. I need you,

52:05.165 --> 52:05.992
you're the only one I trust.

52:06.035 --> 52:08.560
Give me a fuckin' break.

52:08.603 --> 52:11.737
Hey, Dick, she's
always helping you.

52:11.780 --> 52:13.042
I see her here all the time,

52:13.086 --> 52:14.435
she's cleaning up after you,

52:14.479 --> 52:16.872
taking out your garbage,
getting you groceries.

52:17.743 --> 52:20.180
Maybe if you stopped staring
at yourself all damn day,

52:20.224 --> 52:22.008
you'd see how much
she does for you.

52:23.401 --> 52:24.663
- Well.

52:24.706 --> 52:26.055
- You're no better, missy.

52:26.099 --> 52:28.667
Oh, I'm too scared to tell
him how I really feel.

52:28.710 --> 52:30.016
Can't live my own life,

52:30.059 --> 52:33.106
so I guess I'll just
die up here on my cross.

52:33.150 --> 52:34.803
You both suck.

52:34.847 --> 52:36.022
- Well, fuck you, Matt.

52:36.065 --> 52:37.197
- Yeah, fuck you, Matt.

52:37.241 --> 52:38.503
- Fuck me?

52:38.546 --> 52:41.114
- You don't know what
you're talking about.

52:41.158 --> 52:42.811
Why don't you just put a sock
in his mouth or something.

52:42.855 --> 52:43.682
- Is that true?

52:44.857 --> 52:46.424
- No, I mean.

52:46.467 --> 52:48.469
- I don't want you to
be afraid to talk to me.

52:48.513 --> 52:50.471
- Richie, I'm not, it's just.

52:51.603 --> 52:53.170
I'm not, I want to be
able to talk to you.

52:53.213 --> 52:54.606
I want to be able
to tell you things.

52:54.649 --> 52:57.174
- [Richie] Yeah, you should,
I mean, we're siblings,

52:57.217 --> 52:58.262
we should be able to
talk about anything.

52:58.305 --> 52:59.785
- [Becca] I can
trust you, I know,

52:59.828 --> 53:02.701
it's just, it's hard, you know.

53:02.744 --> 53:03.963
- You're goin' to
fuckin' jail, idiots.

53:04.006 --> 53:05.138
- Will you shut up.

53:05.921 --> 53:07.445
- I don't know who
taught you to tie a knot,

53:07.488 --> 53:09.229
but you can add that to the
list of things you suck at.

53:09.273 --> 53:11.144
- See, we should
have just killed him.

53:11.188 --> 53:12.014
- We're not killing anybody.

53:12.058 --> 53:13.712
- You're not killing me.

53:13.755 --> 53:15.192
'Cause you're already dead.

53:16.105 --> 53:18.630
[electricity sizzling]
[Matt groaning]

53:18.673 --> 53:21.110
[body thuds]

53:22.895 --> 53:25.637
- [Becca] Matt, Matt! [groaning]

53:25.680 --> 53:26.681
- [Richie] What are you doing?

53:26.725 --> 53:28.379
- [Becca] What
does it look like?

53:28.422 --> 53:29.684
Matt!

53:29.728 --> 53:30.990
Call 911.

53:31.033 --> 53:31.817
- [Richie] Why would I do that?

53:31.860 --> 53:32.774
Just let him die.

53:32.818 --> 53:33.732
- [Becca] Now!

53:34.602 --> 53:35.386
[ominous whooshing]

53:35.429 --> 53:36.561
- See, it's happening.

53:36.604 --> 53:38.650
You're wasting your
time, he's dead.

53:38.693 --> 53:40.782
[fluid squelching]

53:40.826 --> 53:41.653
See!

53:43.132 --> 53:43.959
I told you.

53:45.265 --> 53:48.442
[fluid squelching]

53:48.486 --> 53:49.922
Stop.

53:49.965 --> 53:51.750
He's dead, you're
wasting your time.

53:52.925 --> 53:54.143
- No.

53:54.187 --> 53:55.275
- We'll switch his clothes.

53:55.319 --> 53:56.450
He won't notice the difference

53:56.494 --> 53:57.495
and it'll be like
it never happened.

53:57.538 --> 53:59.410
- I can't.

53:59.453 --> 54:01.499
- [Richie] Sure
you can, it's easy.

54:01.542 --> 54:02.674
It does not matter.

54:02.717 --> 54:04.545
- No, it does matter, Richie!

54:05.503 --> 54:07.983
These things, they matter.

54:09.376 --> 54:10.551
[Richie sighs]

54:10.595 --> 54:12.510
You keep acting like
nothing's happened.

54:14.425 --> 54:15.382
But I can't.

54:17.341 --> 54:21.127
I carry all of this
shit all the time.

54:22.476 --> 54:23.651
You don't.

54:24.478 --> 54:25.653
You don't care.

54:28.047 --> 54:30.615
[somber music]

54:33.444 --> 54:37.926
I thought you were dead,
back in that hospital.

54:37.970 --> 54:38.971
You remember that?

54:40.320 --> 54:41.365
You were dead.

54:42.366 --> 54:43.584
And then you weren't.

54:45.499 --> 54:49.982
And I thought, why
couldn't he have just died?

54:52.376 --> 54:55.161
Everything would have
been so much easier.

54:58.686 --> 55:01.341
[Becca sobbing]

55:08.000 --> 55:09.436
- Becca, don't think
you need [gasps]--

55:09.480 --> 55:12.309
[Matt gasping]

55:12.352 --> 55:15.050
- [Becca] Oh, oh, okay.

55:15.094 --> 55:16.704
Don't move, don't
move, shh, shh.

55:16.748 --> 55:18.837
- What happened?
- There's been accident.

55:18.880 --> 55:20.055
It's okay.
- It's gone.

55:20.099 --> 55:21.579
- [Matt] What did you do to me?

55:21.622 --> 55:24.930
- Come on, hey, hey,
everything's okay.

55:25.800 --> 55:26.584
[Matt groaning]

55:26.627 --> 55:27.454
- [Richie] Becca.

55:29.674 --> 55:30.849
- You're okay.

55:31.937 --> 55:32.764
- Becca!

55:33.678 --> 55:34.592
- Shh, what?

55:36.376 --> 55:37.769
Hey, you're okay.

55:42.426 --> 55:43.775
Just, just stay there.

55:45.994 --> 55:48.388
- It's gone, where'd it go?

55:49.824 --> 55:50.999
- I don't know.

55:51.043 --> 55:53.001
He's alive, so maybe
it just disappeared.

55:54.046 --> 55:56.744
Okay, get your stuff,
we're going to the hospital

55:56.788 --> 55:57.963
and I'm not leaving
you alone in here.

55:58.006 --> 55:59.356
- No, we can't go to
the hospital, Becca,

55:59.399 --> 56:01.096
because we cannot go--

56:01.140 --> 56:04.273
[Matt screaming]
[ominous music]

56:04.317 --> 56:05.536
- What the hell is, holy fuck!

56:06.928 --> 56:11.933
[monster screaming]
[Becca screaming]

56:12.586 --> 56:14.022
- Don't leave me!

56:17.156 --> 56:20.420
You assholes!
[Richie gasping]

56:20.464 --> 56:24.381
[monster hissing]
[Matt yelling]

56:33.477 --> 56:36.088
[gentle music]

57:07.641 --> 57:12.646
[door squeaking]
[tense music]

57:52.338 --> 57:54.862
[Becca gasping]

57:54.906 --> 57:55.733
Oh shit.

57:57.691 --> 57:58.736
He killed that thing.

58:01.216 --> 58:02.043
- Huh?

58:05.351 --> 58:08.702
- If he got out, we
are in so much trouble.

58:08.746 --> 58:09.921
- That's impossible, you can't--

58:09.964 --> 58:12.532
[Matt gasping]

58:25.850 --> 58:29.201
Dude, that was badass, man,

58:29.244 --> 58:30.942
you crushed that
thing's head in!

58:32.073 --> 58:33.292
All right, listen,

58:33.335 --> 58:34.859
I know this is gonna be
a little overwhelming,

58:34.902 --> 58:36.164
but we can explain everything.

58:36.208 --> 58:37.775
- Richie?

58:37.818 --> 58:38.732
- Hey guys.

58:38.776 --> 58:39.603
- Holy shit!

58:40.560 --> 58:42.867
[men grunting]

58:42.910 --> 58:44.172
Don't touch me!

58:45.304 --> 58:49.482
[screams] Don't touch me!
- Richie!

58:49.526 --> 58:52.180
[men groaning]

58:52.224 --> 58:54.792
- I'm sorry about the music!

58:54.835 --> 58:57.621
[men yelling]

58:57.664 --> 59:01.059
[screaming] Help, Becca!

59:01.102 --> 59:03.017
Becca, help me, Becca!

59:03.061 --> 59:03.888
Becca!

59:05.106 --> 59:06.281
Fuck!

59:06.325 --> 59:07.413
Go, go, go!

59:07.456 --> 59:12.200
[Becca screaming]
[flesh squelching]

59:14.551 --> 59:17.205
[Becca gasping]

59:32.220 --> 59:33.874
- It's fine, it's fine.

59:35.397 --> 59:37.312
He'll come back and we'll
just explain everything to him

59:37.356 --> 59:41.882
so that we avoid, you
know, all of this.

59:44.276 --> 59:45.582
- What happened?

59:47.758 --> 59:50.761
- He came through, but the
old him was still alive,

59:50.804 --> 59:53.590
so I think something must
have gotten corrupted.

59:55.896 --> 59:58.725
They're both dead
now, so. [gasping]

01:00:02.816 --> 01:00:05.471
Maybe we should clear
him out, you know,

01:00:05.514 --> 01:00:07.125
before he comes back.

01:00:07.168 --> 01:00:08.605
Might be a bit of a shocker.

01:00:11.129 --> 01:00:14.132
[tense music]

01:00:14.175 --> 01:00:16.264
All right, grab his legs.

01:00:21.182 --> 01:00:23.837
[Becca gasping]

01:00:25.186 --> 01:00:27.319
- What's happening?
- I don't know.

01:00:27.362 --> 01:00:29.060
- Why isn't it coming out?

01:00:29.103 --> 01:00:31.149
- I don't know.

01:00:31.192 --> 01:00:33.847
[Becca gasping]

01:00:46.599 --> 01:00:48.122
This has never happened before.

01:00:48.166 --> 01:00:49.646
Obviously, I'm still here.

01:00:53.824 --> 01:00:55.608
- Is there anything
in there about me?

01:00:58.567 --> 01:00:59.612
- Why would there be something--

01:00:59.656 --> 01:01:03.268
- Stop, I found
it, in the closet.

01:01:07.925 --> 01:01:10.362
- [sighs] I was trying
to tell you, it's just--

01:01:10.405 --> 01:01:11.276
- [Becca] What did you do?

01:01:11.319 --> 01:01:12.712
- I didn't do anything, Becca.

01:01:12.756 --> 01:01:14.975
But you just need to listen.

01:01:15.019 --> 01:01:18.065
Becca, okay, I just, you,

01:01:22.417 --> 01:01:25.072
it was this.

01:01:27.640 --> 01:01:30.904
I made it for me, this
is what I drank earlier.

01:01:32.427 --> 01:01:34.734
[Becca groans]

01:01:34.778 --> 01:01:37.955
[tape rewinding]

01:01:37.998 --> 01:01:40.697
- Did I come out of
that fucking wall?

01:01:40.740 --> 01:01:42.263
- At first I thought
that you were asleep.

01:01:42.307 --> 01:01:43.656
And then it started happening.

01:01:43.700 --> 01:01:45.223
So I took your clothes and
I put you in the closet.

01:01:45.266 --> 01:01:46.877
I just, I panicked.

01:01:46.920 --> 01:01:48.748
- You stuffed my
body into a closet

01:01:48.792 --> 01:01:50.097
and you didn't even
tell me, Richie.

01:01:50.141 --> 01:01:52.143
- So what, okay, this is
you, this is still you.

01:01:52.186 --> 01:01:53.274
What's the big deal?

01:01:53.318 --> 01:01:54.754
- What's the big deal?

01:01:54.798 --> 01:01:57.278
- We spent the night
cutting up my bodies

01:01:57.322 --> 01:01:58.802
and dumping them in the garbage.

01:01:58.845 --> 01:02:00.151
All of those me's.

01:02:00.194 --> 01:02:01.718
Who gives a shit?

01:02:01.761 --> 01:02:02.893
I'm still here.

01:02:07.288 --> 01:02:09.943
[Becca sighing]

01:02:11.249 --> 01:02:12.424
Becca, where are you going?

01:02:12.467 --> 01:02:13.860
- No, I am done helping you.

01:02:13.904 --> 01:02:15.166
- Becca, don't.

01:02:16.428 --> 01:02:19.170
[dramatic music]

01:02:20.867 --> 01:02:23.565
[Becca moaning]

01:02:24.871 --> 01:02:26.960
- You can't leave!

01:02:27.004 --> 01:02:28.440
And neither can I, okay.

01:02:28.483 --> 01:02:32.618
When it happens,
you're just stuck.

01:02:35.664 --> 01:02:37.057
I figured that out early on.

01:02:40.713 --> 01:02:41.932
- You piece of shit.

01:02:43.063 --> 01:02:44.282
[hand slaps]

01:02:44.325 --> 01:02:49.330
[Becca sobbing]
[somber music]

01:04:04.231 --> 01:04:07.147
[range clicking]

01:04:17.723 --> 01:04:19.464
- [Richie] Becca, I--

01:04:19.507 --> 01:04:22.119
- It's not like I was ever
getting out anyway, right?

01:04:26.123 --> 01:04:28.734
[somber music]

01:04:42.661 --> 01:04:43.749
You know, Mom was
supposed to take me

01:04:43.792 --> 01:04:46.012
to the Oceanarium
in Hampton Beach.

01:04:49.363 --> 01:04:54.368
And then you got
sick, so we didn't go.

01:04:58.242 --> 01:05:00.331
I came home and stayed
with you all night.

01:05:09.514 --> 01:05:12.604
That was the last
time we were there.

01:05:14.084 --> 01:05:15.824
We never went back
after she died.

01:05:27.227 --> 01:05:29.882
And then after you threw
up on Darryl at my prom,

01:05:31.318 --> 01:05:32.624
everybody ditched me.

01:05:37.498 --> 01:05:40.719
So I left early and came
home to check on you.

01:05:49.728 --> 01:05:54.341
When I got that
acceptance letter,

01:05:54.385 --> 01:05:56.735
I couldn't believe I got in.

01:06:11.793 --> 01:06:13.534
I don't even know why I applied.

01:06:19.018 --> 01:06:23.936
It's like I was pretending my
life could be something else.

01:06:27.070 --> 01:06:28.375
I lied to myself.

01:06:31.813 --> 01:06:32.684
And I lied to you.

01:06:46.089 --> 01:06:47.090
Matt was right.

01:06:51.616 --> 01:06:53.183
We really do deserve each other.

01:06:55.185 --> 01:06:56.099
Look at us.

01:07:09.199 --> 01:07:11.070
Can I borrow some pyjama pants?

01:07:11.114 --> 01:07:12.332
I gotta get out of these.

01:07:22.038 --> 01:07:24.518
Would you give it
a rest, please?

01:07:25.824 --> 01:07:26.825
- I figured it out.

01:07:30.394 --> 01:07:31.264
- Lay it on me.

01:07:34.050 --> 01:07:38.750
- The brain. It didn't come
back because we got his brain.

01:07:42.754 --> 01:07:45.757
You can't make a copy once the
master copy is gone, right.

01:07:45.800 --> 01:07:46.845
We break the pattern.

01:07:48.542 --> 01:07:49.369
- Richie.

01:07:50.414 --> 01:07:52.155
- None of this was
my original plan.

01:07:54.592 --> 01:07:55.941
I didn't want to come back.

01:08:49.515 --> 01:08:50.560
- Jesus, Richie is that--

01:08:50.604 --> 01:08:51.430
- Dad's rifle.

01:08:52.519 --> 01:08:53.607
This is how it ends.

01:08:56.219 --> 01:09:00.091
And then maybe,
maybe you can leave.

01:09:00.136 --> 01:09:00.919
- And maybe not.

01:09:01.876 --> 01:09:03.225
Maybe that's not
what's gonna happen.

01:09:03.269 --> 01:09:05.270
Maybe you'll end
up like that thing.

01:09:05.314 --> 01:09:06.142
- I doubt it.

01:09:09.100 --> 01:09:11.321
This is all my fault.

01:09:11.363 --> 01:09:12.191
I'm the cause.

01:09:12.234 --> 01:09:13.279
You're caught up in my loop.

01:09:13.323 --> 01:09:16.020
So maybe, if I
close it for good,

01:09:17.370 --> 01:09:18.893
then you can walk out of here.

01:09:23.680 --> 01:09:26.162
- I can't let you do that.

01:09:26.205 --> 01:09:28.859
Look, I didn't mean
what I said before.

01:09:30.557 --> 01:09:34.518
- This is not a life.

01:09:34.560 --> 01:09:36.345
- I can help you.

01:09:36.389 --> 01:09:38.304
- This is not a
life for you, Becca.

01:09:41.568 --> 01:09:42.961
And you deserve to have one.

01:09:49.837 --> 01:09:51.055
Can I show you something?

01:10:05.462 --> 01:10:07.986
[Becca sighs]

01:10:13.992 --> 01:10:14.906
Take a closer look.

01:10:33.794 --> 01:10:35.143
What do you see?

01:10:36.928 --> 01:10:37.755
- I don't know.

01:10:41.628 --> 01:10:43.151
I still see an asshole.

01:10:45.241 --> 01:10:46.067
- Exactly.

01:10:48.766 --> 01:10:51.247
[lock clicks]

01:10:54.511 --> 01:10:55.338
- Richie!

01:10:56.382 --> 01:10:57.340
Open the door!

01:11:06.958 --> 01:11:08.786
- That is all I see

01:11:08.829 --> 01:11:13.530
when I look at myself
is one giant asshole.

01:11:17.403 --> 01:11:19.231
I know how much
you've done for me,

01:11:19.275 --> 01:11:23.888
how much you do and it kills me

01:11:24.758 --> 01:11:27.108
that you couldn't share
such good news with me.

01:11:32.940 --> 01:11:36.944
I have been trying for so
long to get better for you.

01:11:43.255 --> 01:11:46.911
But I'm tired, Becca, I'm tired

01:11:46.954 --> 01:11:49.261
and I don't want to
feel like this anymore.

01:11:52.699 --> 01:11:56.616
I've been cutting
myself up into pieces,

01:11:56.660 --> 01:11:59.880
trying to put them back
in a way that works.

01:12:00.881 --> 01:12:02.143
But I can't.

01:12:02.187 --> 01:12:05.016
And then this crazy
thing starts happening.

01:12:06.713 --> 01:12:11.239
And I think, maybe, maybethere could be a better version

01:12:11.283 --> 01:12:13.329
of me somewhere in there.

01:12:14.330 --> 01:12:18.595
But every time I come
back, I'm the exact same,

01:12:20.423 --> 01:12:22.338
the exact fucking same, just me.

01:12:49.016 --> 01:12:50.235
I'm proud of you.

01:12:52.716 --> 01:12:55.371
I am so proud of you

01:12:57.547 --> 01:12:59.549
for taking a chance on yourself

01:12:59.592 --> 01:13:02.290
and proving that you can
have the life that you want.

01:13:08.035 --> 01:13:10.734
This is gonna work, I know it

01:13:10.777 --> 01:13:12.649
and then you can go

01:13:12.692 --> 01:13:14.825
and there will be
nothing holding you back.

01:13:19.046 --> 01:13:21.962
And you'll be great and you're
gonna help so many people.

01:13:24.748 --> 01:13:26.097
- I can take care of you.

01:13:27.098 --> 01:13:29.187
I can, I know it.

01:13:31.842 --> 01:13:32.712
- You have.

01:13:36.629 --> 01:13:39.284
This is not on
you, little sister.

01:13:41.155 --> 01:13:45.116
It's on me, it's
always been on me.

01:13:46.596 --> 01:13:47.945
Just try to remember that.

01:13:48.815 --> 01:13:50.338
- You don't hold me back.

01:13:51.252 --> 01:13:53.907
And you don't have to do this.

01:13:53.951 --> 01:13:56.736
You don't have to do this.

01:13:56.780 --> 01:14:00.827
Please, I need you in my life.

01:14:00.871 --> 01:14:02.916
It's not the same without you.

01:14:02.960 --> 01:14:05.528
[fist tapping]

01:14:06.703 --> 01:14:09.357
- I love you.

01:14:09.401 --> 01:14:10.358
I love you so much.

01:14:14.232 --> 01:14:15.059
- No.

01:14:17.104 --> 01:14:17.931
Richie!

01:14:21.282 --> 01:14:22.153
No.

01:14:22.196 --> 01:14:23.720
[dramatic music]

01:14:23.763 --> 01:14:26.679
[door rattling]
No.

01:14:29.377 --> 01:14:30.204
Richie!

01:14:32.903 --> 01:14:34.252
No, turn it off!

01:14:36.733 --> 01:14:41.302
[gun firing]
[Becca whimpering]

01:14:41.346 --> 01:14:42.173
No.

01:14:46.656 --> 01:14:49.354
[Becca sobbing]

01:14:54.446 --> 01:14:55.795
[dramatic music]

01:14:55.839 --> 01:14:56.666
No.

01:15:14.901 --> 01:15:15.728
Come on!

01:15:18.122 --> 01:15:18.949
Be wrong!

01:15:28.524 --> 01:15:29.350
Come on.

01:16:01.600 --> 01:16:02.514
Goddam you!

01:16:05.169 --> 01:16:07.998
[hammer thudding]

01:16:19.662 --> 01:16:22.360
[Becca gasping]

01:16:31.587 --> 01:16:34.720
[loud dramatic music]

01:17:35.128 --> 01:17:37.696
[upbeat music]

01:18:09.162 --> 01:18:12.383
[bright upbeat music]
